  "software_requirements": [
    "rpm",
    "bash",

    "scalasca (optional)",
    "prun",
    "readlink",
    "awk",
    "grep"
  ],
  "resource_requirements": [
    "PBS or Slurm resource manager",
    "access to a cluster with nodes",
    "access to a shared file system for job output"
  ]
}
